creator: Talking Animals
descriptionHtml:
In this cool free talking game, the famous pet Rhinois going on an amazing life adventure!

THE MOST BEAUTIFUL ENVIRONMENT：Talking Rhinohas a living room, a bedroom, a restaurant, a large lawn and a forest.

EVERYDAY FUN: His bathroom is great, where he can take a bath. Wipe with him with a towel, so that the Rhino is more clean and more lovely! There is a great bedroom great, he can turn off the lights there, full rest! We go to his living room, the sofa in front of you will see the lovely little Rhino. Play tired, remember to feed Rhino to eat, a variety of food choices.

NEW MINI GAMES: Multiple puzzle games, Math,Memory,Feeding,JumpRocket,Bubble Shoot,Zigzag,CroossRoad,DrawLine,Break.

New RACING GAME: You can drive kinds of cars on the snow or grass ground, or you can race against other cars on the track. To beat them.

INTERACTIVE: Labrador Dog will repeat what you said with interesting sounds. Poke his head, stomach or feet.
